to be there.

25:30.070 --> 25:33.404
To get very drunk indeed,
and dance until she dropped.

25:35.868 --> 25:37.359
Our dancing queen.

25:40.789 --> 25:41.789
Yeah.

25:43.333 --> 25:44.540
It will get better.

25:45.294 --> 25:46.294
Yeah.

25:47.671 --> 25:49.082
