Nothing else can save me</i>

26:20.204 --> 26:22.161
<i>When you're gone</i>

26:23.749 --> 26:30.588
<i>How can I even try to go on?</i>

26:33.592 --> 26:35.800
<i>When you're gone</i>

26:38.597 --> 26:40.964
<i>Though I try</i>

26:43.727 --> 26:49.644
<i>How can I carry on?</i>

27:00.828 --> 27:01.864
Hey.

27:12.798 --> 27:15.381
You grew your hair.
It's longer now.

27:16.343 --> 27:18.380
It is a bit. Yeah.

27:18.929 --> 27:23.594
I know we could talk about that,
but the ferry leaves any second,

27:23.684 --> 27:26.768
and I think great things
are waiting for me.

27:28.147 --> 27:29.228
I prefer it shorter.

27:36.864 --> 27:39.026
Wait! Wait!

27:40.325 --> 27:42.908
Please! Don't. Oh, God.

27:42.995 --> 27:46.113
Turn around right now!
It's not too late!

27:48.041 --> 27:49.248
This is great.

27:50.085 --> 27:52.202
I'm just gonna
follow you everywhere.

27:52.296 --> 27:54.504
By the end of the day,
I'll have a whole new wardrobe.

27:55.257 --> 27:56.457
I don't think
that'll suit you.

27:56.800 --> 27:58.257
I say I can make it work.

27:59.094 --> 28:01.006
I really wanted
to catch that ferry.

28:02.556 --> 28:04.092
There'll be another tomorrow.

28:04.183 --> 28:05.390
Thanks.

28:09.271 --> 28:15.108
Right, uh, but what would be really great,
today, not tomorrow,

28:15.527 --> 28:19.271
is if somewhere in this harbor
there was a guy.

28:19.865 --> 28:23.108
Young, tall,
dashingly handsome.

28:23.202 --> 28:25.159
He's probably
passable-looking,

28:26.538 --> 28:27.538
but he has a boat.

28:27.998 --> 28:30.615
And a couple of days free before
he takes part in a sailing race.

28:31.293 --> 28:33.455
So, maybe he could take her
where she wants to go.

28:33.545 --> 28:36.037
He'd love to.
But the sad fact is,

28:37.007 --> 28:39.545
this isn't my boat.
I just wanted to impress you.

28:43.472 --> 28:44.588
Oh, okay.

28:45.140 --> 28:50.056
I'm kidding. I'm kidding.
Jump on. I'm Bill.

28:58.403 --> 29:00.520
I actually have an elderly
relative on the island

29:00.614 --> 29:02.230
who helped me buy this boat.

29:02.824 --> 29:04.156
There are two beds,

29:05.118 --> 29:08.907
but, unfortunately,
one of them's rather full.

29:11.291 --> 29:12.407
Convenient.

29:14.211 --> 29:17.704
You have one of those smiles that
makes the rest of the world smile too.

29:19.091 --> 29:20.673
It's lucky this trip
is not long enough

29:20.759 --> 29:23.718
for my fragile heart to shatter
completely when you leave my boat.

29:24.096 --> 29:27.430
I get it.
You're one of them.

29:29.268 --> 29:30.509
One of who?

29:30.936 --> 29:34.771
There are
two kinds of seducer.

29:36.149 --> 29:42.362
The first doesn't actually like women,
so wants to assert his power over them.

29:42.990 --> 29:46.074
But the second,
and far more dangerous,

29:46.743 --> 29:50.157
is the guy who genuinely
falls in love every evening

29:50.247 --> 29:52.864
only to fall out of it again
the next morning.

29:53.792 --> 29:56.409
But as you run away,
you tell her you're the one in pain

29:56.503 --> 29:59.211
and she's just too much
for you to handle.

29:59.923 --> 30:01.004
Like this?

30:04.928 --> 30:08.467
<i>When you were
lonely You needed a man</i>

30:09.057 --> 30:13.051
<i>Someone to lean on
Well, I understand</i>

30:13.395 --> 30:15.227
<i>It's only natural</i>

30:15.314 --> 30:17.931
<i>But why did it have to be me?</i>

30:18.984 --> 30:20.816
Just like that, yes.

30:21.361 --> 30:25.105
<i>Nights can be empty
And nights can be cold</i>

30:25.657 --> 30:29.651
<i>So you were looking
For someone to hold</i>

30:29.745 --> 30:31.532
<i>That's only natural</i>

30:31.621 --> 30:34.785
<i>But why did it have to be me?</i>

30:38.086 --> 30:41.921
<i>I was so lonesome
I was blue</i>

30:42.007 --> 30:46.718
<i>I couldn't help it
It had to be you and I</i>

30:47.637 --> 30:51.347
<i>Always thought you knew
the reason why</i>

30:51.433 --> 30:52.890
Huh?

30:54.853 --> 30:58.142
<i>I only wanted
A little love affair</i>

30:58.940 --> 31:02.433
<i>Now I can see you are
beginning to care</i>

31:02.527 --> 31:05.736
<i>But, baby, believe me</i>

31:06.698 --> 31:10.692
<i>It's better to forget me</i>

31:14.998 --> 31:17.115
Your hair, it's shorter now.

31:17.667 --> 31:20.747
Well, yes, I had to cut it for work.
I wonder, could you please hurry up a bit?

31:21.254 --> 31:23.246
You see, I followed a girl
all the way from Paris.

31:24.216 --> 31:28.301
She wrote me a note.
A very kind note, saying goodbye.

31:29.471 --> 31:32.054
But when you find the only girl
you think you're ever gonna love

31:32.140 --> 31:35.633
it's gotta be worth one more try.
Don't you think?

31:36.895 --> 31:38.056
It's better short.

31:39.731 --> 31:43.395
<i>Men are the toys
In the game that you play</i>

31:43.777 --> 31:47.270
<i>When you get tired
You throw them away</i>

31:47.864 --> 31:50.026
<i>That's only natural</i>

31:50.117 --> 31:52.450
<i>But why did it have to be me?</i>

32:00.168 --> 32:03.912
<i>Falling in love
With a woman like you</i>

32:04.381 --> 32:07.670
<i>Happens so quickly
There's nothing to do</i>

32:08.301 --> 32:10.088
<i>It's only natural</i>

32:10.178 --> 32:13.012
<i>But why did it have to be me?</i>

32:13.473 --> 32:14.805
We only just met.

32:14.891 --> 32:16.302
And you're not
that kind of girl?

32:16.393 --> 32:18.931
Absolutely not. Usually.

32:19.020 --> 32:20.181
Hey!

32:20.981 --> 32:24.474
- What was that?
- Nothing, a seagull. Now, where were we?

32:25.569 --> 32:27.185
<i>It's only natural</i>

32:28.238 --> 32:30.321
<i>But why did it have to be...</i>

32:30.407 --> 32:31.523
Hey!

32:32.242 --> 32:33.403
Come on!

32:37.789 --> 32:38.996
We're coming.

32:43.753 --> 32:44.753
Hi.

32:45.130 --> 32:46.666
Just checking
you're not in danger,

32:46.756 --> 32:48.497
which you're obviously not,
so we'll be off.

32:48.592 --> 32:49.924
But my engine is not working.

32:50.010 --> 32:53.094
Oh! Oh, that is bad luck.

32:53.180 --> 32:55.046
I'll radio for someone
to come and help you.

32:55.140 --> 32:56.256
They should be along soon.

32:56.808 --> 32:58.015
- Bill.
- Please. Please!

32:58.226 --> 33:00.639
There is a woman waiting for me
on the mainland.

33:01.188 --> 33:04.807
Her family, they not want her to marry
a simple fisherman like Alexio.

33:05.734 --> 33:10.195
They want rich man. Ugly, fat,
big mole on face, but rich.

33:11.364 --> 33:12.364
But she...

33:13.909 --> 33:14.909
She want me.

33:16.161 --> 33:18.995
And I love her
with all my heartness.

33:20.707 --> 33:24.872
Please help, kind sir and beautiful
lady with head full of curls.

33:26.463 --> 33:27.783
Well, obviously,
we're doing this.

33:28.465 --> 33:29.465
- Yes!
- Yes!

33:38.266 --> 33:39.302
There!

33:40.644 --> 33:43.057
I see them.
Okay, everyone, we're nearly...

33:43.146 --> 33:44.432
Apollonia!

33:46.483 --> 33:47.483
Whoa!

33:48.485 --> 33:50.727
What are you doing?
We could get you closer.

33:50.820 --> 33:54.564
If you love someone,
you're willing to die for her!

33:55.283 --> 33:57.991
Yeah, but you don't have to.
It's an important distinction.

33:58.078 --> 33:59.285
Apollonia!

34:00.664 --> 34:01.905
Alexio!

34:01.998 --> 34:03.489
Apollo...

34:03.583 --> 34:05.870
He's just swallowed
a big mouthful of water,

34:05.961 --> 34:08.418
but the basic point he's trying to make
is that he loves you.

34:08.505 --> 34:11.714
- What?
- He loves you!

34:12.842 --> 34:13.922
Apollonia!

34:16.513 --> 34:18.254
Apollonia! Apollonia!

34:19.014 --> 34:21.757
Apollonia! Apollonia!
Come back!

34:34.072 --> 34:35.072
Apollonia!

34:37.993 --> 34:39.029
Apollonia!

34:39.327 --> 34:41.409
- Good work.
- You, too.

34:42.706 --> 34:43.706
I love you!

34:45.917 --> 34:47.658
Oh, God. I don't think
she can swim either.

34:56.844 --> 34:58.552
- Apollonia!
- Whoo!

34:59.848 --> 35:01.158
- Good morning.
- Good morning.

35:01.182 --> 35:04.262
- Oh, good morning. It's so nice. Guys.
- I'm glad you like it.

35:04.311 --> 35:07.145
I do. And these are perfect.
Everything is.

35:07.230 --> 35:08.230
Thank you.

35:08.315 --> 35:11.433
It's so good.
It's all so amazing.

35:11.526 --> 35:12.812
If you are happy...

35:12.902 --> 35:15.019
I would be even happier
if you were happy.

35:15.113 --> 35:17.821
No happiness for me.
As you say, that ship sailed

35:18.742 --> 35:19.949
many long years ago.

35:20.493 --> 35:23.986
But ships turn around.
They come back.

35:24.080 --> 35:25.196
Not for me.

35:25.624 --> 35:28.583
She left, never to return.

35:28.960 --> 35:33.045
But don't you worry.
I have made my peace with pain.

35:33.548 --> 35:35.164
You and me both, <i>Se√±or.</i>

35:39.012 --> 35:40.093
What? What is it?

35:41.389 --> 35:42.389
I'm not sure.

35:43.725 --> 35:46.012
- Tell me.
- I fear a storm is coming.

35:50.690 --> 35:52.170
You sure
you're okay here?

35:53.610 --> 35:54.610
Yeah, I'll be fine.

35:55.195 --> 35:57.061
I'll come right back
after the race.

35:58.698 --> 36:00.189
But that won't be
for three weeks.

36:00.283 --> 36:01.523
Look at this place.

36:02.369 --> 36:03.369
Isn't it beautiful?

36:04.162 --> 36:05.162
It is, yeah.

36:06.873 --> 36:08.364
What? What's wrong?

36:09.292 --> 36:10.499
Storm is coming.

36:10.919 --> 36:12.455
It's a clear sky.

36:12.671 --> 36:15.459
Trust me.
Actually, don't.

36:16.341 --> 36:17.502
But I know I'm right.

36:17.884 --> 36:19.000
I'll still be fine.

36:21.096 --> 36:22.507
I got a very good feeling.

36:34.234 --> 36:36.476
And you and Sam
did all of this?

36:36.569 --> 36:37.569
We had some help.

36:37.696 --> 36:38.696
From Sky.

36:39.280 --> 36:42.569
Right. Yes, right.
And there is more.

36:44.953 --> 36:45.953
Hello?

36:49.249 --> 36:50.249
Hello!

36:54.838 --> 36:56.249
<i>How did she know?</i>

36:57.090 --> 36:58.090
How did Donna know?

36:58.591 --> 36:59.591
What?

37:00.427 --> 37:02.089
That that could be this?

37:02.595 --> 37:06.054
I guess she just saw
the future.

37:11.604 --> 37:15.644
<i>I have a dream</i>

37:16.317 --> 37:19.355
<i>A song to sing</i>

37:21.072 --> 37:24.816
<i>To help me cope</i>

37:25.827 --> 37:28.820
<i>With anything</i>

37:31.166 --> 37:34.580
<i>If you see the wonder</i>

37:36.004 --> 37:38.212
<i>Of a fairy-tale</i>

37:40.633 --> 37:44.126
<i>You can take the future</i>

37:45.513 --> 37:48.756
<i>Even if you fail</i>

37:50.059 --> 37:53.473
<i>I believe in angels</i>

37:54.689 --> 37:59.684
<i>Something good
