37:59.778 --> 38:03.237
<i>I believe in angels</i>

38:04.365 --> 38:08.609
<i>When I know the time
is right for me</i>

38:09.078 --> 38:12.321
<i>Across the stream</i>

38:13.625 --> 38:17.164
<i>I have a dream</i>

38:18.129 --> 38:22.544
<i>I have a dream</i>

38:22.634 --> 38:27.299
<i>A fantasy</i>

38:27.388 --> 38:30.051
<i>To help me through</i>

38:37.190 --> 38:41.104
<i>And my destination</i>

38:41.694 --> 38:45.608
<i>Makes it worth the while</i>

38:46.366 --> 38:50.280
<i>Pushing through the darkness</i>

38:50.995 --> 38:54.830
<i>Still another mile</i>

38:58.962 --> 39:00.248
Do you think she'd like it?

39:00.505 --> 39:02.588
- Oh, Sophie.
- Sophie.

39:04.467 --> 39:07.255
Oh, no.
He said this might happen.

39:24.070 --> 39:25.070
Hello.

39:40.086 --> 39:41.086
Hey.

39:41.421 --> 39:42.457
Whoa.

39:52.181 --> 39:54.719
Wait there, okay?
I'll be back, okay?

40:08.197 --> 40:09.608
Stop! Stop!

40:10.700 --> 40:11.816
Can I help?

40:15.705 --> 40:17.662
I've got it!
Tie up the ropes!

40:24.130 --> 40:25.130
You got it?

40:30.553 --> 40:33.296
- You got a plan?
- Oh, absolutely. I'm a trained veterinarian.

40:33.765 --> 40:35.927
- Really?
- No. No, I'm an architect.

40:36.017 --> 40:37.883
But don't tell this guy that.

40:37.977 --> 40:39.468
- Whoa. Okay.
- Whoa.

40:39.562 --> 40:41.303
I'll distract him.
You grab the halter.

40:41.397 --> 40:43.855
Good plan.
What's the halter?

40:45.526 --> 40:46.642
Just talk calmly.

40:47.153 --> 40:48.360
Easier when I'm calm.

40:49.030 --> 40:50.271
All right, my friend.

40:50.615 --> 40:51.947
Storms are scary.

40:52.325 --> 40:56.114
And I wish I was home and dry right now,
too, but believe me,

40:56.537 --> 41:00.872
if it came down to a choice between
leaving you and helping you,

41:00.959 --> 41:03.542
there's no choice at all.

41:05.922 --> 41:08.164
Good boy. Good boy.

41:08.716 --> 41:11.379
Good boy. Good boy.

41:21.062 --> 41:24.976
So, uh, we've walked the entire island.
I still haven't seen where you live.

41:26.025 --> 41:28.233
In a shack on a hill.

41:30.154 --> 41:31.634
And what the hell
are you doing there?

41:31.906 --> 41:34.319
Uh... I don't know.
Running away, I guess.

41:35.702 --> 41:37.694
Back home everything
was lined up for me.

41:38.204 --> 41:42.198
A great job and just, you know,
my whole life mapped out.

41:43.459 --> 41:45.419
I wanted to take a break
before I signed up to it.

41:45.920 --> 41:46.956
How about you?

41:48.923 --> 41:51.040
I have absolutely
nothing mapped out.

41:52.051 --> 41:53.792
And no clue
what the future holds.

41:55.304 --> 41:56.886
Enough walking. Let's ride.

42:13.614 --> 42:18.325
So, how come you're here
all alone, saving horses?

42:18.411 --> 42:21.279
Uh, I've been
traveling all my life.

42:21.372 --> 42:25.457
My dad was never in the picture,
and my mom's always on tour.

42:25.543 --> 42:26.659
Oh. She sings?

42:26.753 --> 42:28.494
Sweet as sugarcane.

42:30.131 --> 42:32.544
You know, there's some
great stuff here.

42:33.342 --> 42:35.129
This dress would look
very pretty on...

42:36.387 --> 42:37.969
You really don't know me
at all, do you?

42:38.806 --> 42:40.013
<i>Okay.</i>

42:40.767 --> 42:41.974
<i>Hey!</i>

42:42.518 --> 42:45.977
<i>Kisses of fire
Burning, burning</i>

42:46.064 --> 42:49.478
<i>I'm at the point of
no returning</i>

42:49.567 --> 42:53.186
<i>Kisses of fire,
sweet devotions</i>

42:53.279 --> 42:58.695
<i>Caught in a landslide
of emotions</i>

42:58.785 --> 43:00.572
<i>I've had my share
of love affairs</i>

43:00.661 --> 43:03.825
<i>But they were nothing
compared to this</i>

43:03.915 --> 43:05.998
<i>Ooh</i>

43:06.084 --> 43:07.950
<i>I'm riding higher than the sky</i>

43:08.044 --> 43:09.535
<i>and there is fire
in every kiss...</i>

43:09.629 --> 43:10.915
